					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">When you turn off the screen are you also disabling NMI? NMI I believe still occurs even if you disable rendering. So you can still time your music updates that way, but you'll need your NMI routine to know not to do its own PPU updates or anything else that would interfere.
<br />
<br />Edit: Oh I didn't even realize when I pulled up the thread that this was the GB. However it might still be true.</div>

